30
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:54,380
All the outside things could ruin a relationship that is just beginning, you know?

31
00:01:55,180 --> 00:01:57,060
And that's our problem.

32
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:00,800
That we allow

33
