- Always did it.

34
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:08,860
I mean, Eva trying to control us,

35
00:02:09,220 --> 00:02:12,740
Lucho getting mad at you. I mean--

36
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:17,400
Do whatever you want. If you want to be with Juliana and that makes you happy,

37
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,560
Do it.

38
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:22,060
Me too. If i want to be with Renata, then that's it.

39
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:26,740
- Yeah. Yeah.
- So, what?

40
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:29,820
- They manipulate us. That's--
- Uh-huh. Exactly.

41
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:33,620
I'm happy that you made this decision, honestly.

42
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:37,340
We're good. You and I, we're good. Here.

